     <body>
     <div type="poem" subtype="to_the__reader">
   <head>Ad Candidum Lectorem.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>REs gestas si scire voles ab origine mundi,</l>
      <l>Sacra prophetarū fac monumēta legas.</l>
      <l>Historias si ritè cupis perstingere: cures</l>
      <l>Singula temporibus disposuisse suis.</l>
      <l>Annorum seriem facili contexere filo,</l>
      <l>Si cupis: huc adsis, hunc lege, doctus eris.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>S. C.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
